      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，预评估就是train-then-test的在线模式。那PerformanceEvaluator是独立参与者吗？还是算在PrequentialEvaluator内部？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PerformanceEvaluator",
        "PrequentialEvaluator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "PerformanceEvaluator是独立的，PrequentialEvaluator会把预测结果传给它，让它累积性能指标。另外还需要一个循环，条件是processed小于max_instances。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PerformanceEvaluator",
        "loop",
        "processed",
        "max_instances"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个参与者摆好：PrequentialEvaluator、Stream、Classifier、PerformanceEvaluator。循环框也画上了，里面第一步是PE调用ST的next_instance()。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PrequentialEvaluator",
        "Stream",
        "Classifier",
        "PerformanceEvaluator",
        "loop",
        "next_instance"
