    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，ST返回inst（DenseInstance）给PE，然后PE发消息给CL获取votes。接下来PE把inst和votes一起发给PerformanceEvaluator？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DenseInstance",
        "inst",
        "votes",
        "PerformanceEvaluator"
