      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "训练步骤加好了。我注意到有两个采样逻辑：一个是按sample_frequency记录curve，另一个是按mem_check_frequency检查内存。这两个都是alt条件分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
